text: Depending on the User's specific device, this Application may request certain permissions that allow it to access the User's device Data as described below.
In general, Presults may collect, process, store,  transmit, and disseminate only that private information that is necessary for the proper  functioning of its business.
If User grants any of the permissions listed below, the respective Personal Data may be processed (i.e accessed to, modified or removed) by this Application.
